                            <comment id="15200262" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Thu, 17 Mar 2016 20:01:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s an updated patch that modifies a random range test to include docs w/o a value in the field and also queries across negative values.&lt;/p&gt;

